      Associate Specialist at The Global Fund, where I lead global reporting on key performance indicators,
      impact data systems, and programmatic results.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg">
      My core strengths include data analysis, program evaluation, stakeholder engagement, and strengthening
      health systems through evidence-informed strategies. I’ve collaborated with WHO, UNAIDS, DFID,
      and national governments to build resilient public health infrastructures.
    </p>
